name: 11th World Congress on Breast Cancer & Therapies
content: Conference Series llc LTD invites all the participants from all over the world to attend "11th World Congress on Breast Cancer & Therapies" during May 24-25, 2021 at Amsterdam, Netherlands. Which includes prompt keynote presentations, Oral talks, Poster presentations and Exhibitions. The theme of the conference is “Together We Can Make a Difference against Breast Cancer” promises an outstanding scientific program featuring many well-known and thought-provoking speakers.
